NOW THEREFORE, THE PARTIES HEREBY AGREE AS FOLLOWS: 
1 
Definitions and Interpretation 
1.1 
Definitions 
In this Agreement, the following terms shall have the following meanings unless the context 
otherwise requires: 
“2014 ICL-Vodafone MSA” has the meaning given to that term in Schedule 5 (Standard Site 
Access Terms); 
“Acquisition Lead Time” has the meaning given to that term in Schedule 1 (Site Access 
Availability);  
“Active Infrastructure” located at a telecommunications site includes the base terminal station 
equipment, associated antennae, base station controller, RNC mobile switching centre, backhaul 
connectivity to the Sharing Operator’s network and other requisite equipment and associated 
civil and electrical works required to provide telecommunications services by such Sharing 
Operator at such telecommunications site;  
“Additional Charges” has the meaning given to that term in Schedule 3 (Charges);  
“Additional Free Exit Entitlement” has the meaning given to that term in Schedule 5 (Standard 
Site Access Terms); 
“Affected Party” has the meaning given to that term in Clause 16.1; 
“Agreement” has the meaning given to that term in the Preamble; 
“Applicable Rate” has the meaning given to that term in Schedule 3 (Charges);  
“Approved Contractor” means a person or team of persons (including the Sharing Operator and 
its employees) who holds a valid approval from the Sharing Operator to serve the requirements 
of the Sharing Operator in accordance with the applicable Service Contract as being properly 
trained, qualified and experienced to carry out the kind of activities permitted by the Service 
Contract; 
“Arbitration Rules” has the meaning given to that term in Clause 20.2; 
“BTS” means Base Transceiver Station, part of the Active Infrastructure, deployed by the Sharing 
Operator to establish the wireless communication between the customer’s mobile handset and 
such Sharing Operator’s network; 
“Business Day” in relation to a Site, means a day other than a Saturday, Sunday or public or bank 
holiday in the city or state in India where such Site is located; 
“Business Transfer Agreement” means the Business Transfer Agreement executed among the

Confidential 
