“Material Defects” shall have the meaning given to that term in Schedule 1 (Site Access 
Availability) and any defect leading to non-fulfilment of Uptime Service levels;  
“Merger” has the meaning given to that term in Schedule 5 (Standard Site Access Terms); 
“New Build Sites” mean the new Sites (where no existing infrastructure is currently available) to 
be built by the PI company and provided to the Sharing Operator at the request of the Sharing 
Operator, on or after the Effective Date; 
“New Sites” means the Sites (other than the Existing Sites) which shall be provided to the 
Sharing Operator post the Effective Date in accordance with Schedule 1 (Site Access Availability);  
“New Service Orders” has the meaning given to that term in Schedule 5 (Standard Site Access 
Terms); 
“NOC” has the meaning given to that term in Schedule 2(Operations and Maintenance Services);   
“Non-Territory Circles” means and includes the following Circles: Mumbai, Delhi, Haryana, 
Rajasthan, Maharashtra and Goa, Uttar Pradesh East, Uttar Pradesh West, Gujarat, Tamil Nadu, 
Chennai, Karnataka, Andhra Pradesh, Punjab, Kerala, Kolkata and West Bengal;  
“Notice” has the meaning given to that term in Clause 22.6.1; 
“Operation and Maintenance Service Credits” means the service credits relating to Operation 
and Maintenance Services as set out in Schedule 2 (Operation and Maintenance Services); 
“Operation and Maintenance Service Levels” means the service levels relating to Operation and 
Maintenance Services as set out in Schedule 2 (Operation and Maintenance Services); 
“Operation and Maintenance Services” means those services set out in Schedule 2 (Operations 
and Maintenance Services);   
“Other Party” has the meaning given to that term in Clause 16.1.1; 
“Party” or “Parties” has the meaning given to that term in the Preamble; 
“PI company” has the meaning given to that term in the Preamble; 
“PI Company Confirmation” has the meaning given to that term in Schedule 1 (Site Access 
Availability); 
“PI Company Downtime” has the meaning given to that term in Schedule 2 (Operations and 
Maintenance Services);   
“Passive Infrastructure” means the tower, room/shelter, air-conditioning, diesel generator and 
associated electrical and civil works located at a Site which is owned and operated by the PI 
company, but shall not, in any event, include the Active Infrastructure located at such Site;  
“Permit” means any permission, clearance, concession, license, authorisation, consent, permit, 
exemption, no-objection or approval of whatsoever nature obtained or required to be obtained 
from any Government Authority or any third party by any Party in accordance with applicable 
Laws, in connection with the existence or operation of this Agreement or any Site or the conduct

Confidential 
